org.openhab.binding.velux.internal

Class VeluxBindingConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.VeluxBindingConstants

  • @NonNullByDefault
public class VeluxBindingConstants
extends java.lang.Object
    The VeluxBindingConstants class defines common constants, which are used across the whole binding.

    For an in-depth view of the available Item types with description of parameters, take a look onto VeluxItemType.

    This class contains the Thing identifications:
    • THING_VELUX_BRIDGE for the bridge itself,
    • THING_VELUX_SCENE for the scenes summarizing a set of actuator states,
    • THING_VELUX_ACTUATOR for the general actuators identified on the bridge,
    • THING_VELUX_ROLLERSHUTTER for the rollershutters identified on the bridge,
    • THING_VELUX_WINDOW for the windows identified on the bridge.
    • THING_VELUX_VSHUTTER for the virtual shutters defined in the configuration
    Author:
    Guenther Schreiner - Initial contribution
